-word word="zadok"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #0000FF;">Zadok</span></x-word> and <x-word word="abiathar"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #0000FF;">Abiathar</span></x-word> the priests? therefore it shall be, that what thing <x-word word="soever"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #0000FF;">soever</span></x-word> <x-group group="thouXshalt"><span style="box-shadow: 0px 3px white, 0px 4px #00BFFF;">thou <x-word word="shalt"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #800000;">shalt</span></x-word></span></x-group> hear out of the king's house, <x-group group="thouXshalt"><span style="box-shadow: 0px 3px white, 0px 4px #00BFFF;">thou <x-word word="shalt"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #800000;">shalt</span></x-word></span></x-group> tell it to Zadok and <x-word word="abiathar"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #0000FF;">Abiathar</span></x-word> the priests.<br>祭司撒督和亚比亚他，岂不都在那里吗？你在王宫里听见什么，就要告诉祭司撒督和亚比亚他。<br><br><br>撒下15:36 <br><x-word word="behold"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">Behold</span></x-word>, they have there with them their two sons, <x-word word="ahimaaz"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #0000FF;">Ahimaaz</span></x-word> Zadok's son, and <x-word word="jonathan"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">Jonathan</span></x-word> Abiathar's son; and by them ye shall send unto me every thing that ye can hear.<br>撒督的儿子亚希玛斯，亚比亚他的儿子约拿单，也都在那里。凡你们所听见的，可以托这二人来报告我。”<br><br><br>撒下15:37 <br>So <x-word word="hushai"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #0000FF;">Hushai</span></x-word> David's friend came into the city, and Absalom came into <x-word word="jerusalem"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">Jerusalem</span></x-word>.<br>于是，大卫的朋友户筛进了城；押沙龙也进了耶路撒冷。</p>

